items.name: Chevrolet Niva
items.description:
LADA Niva Travel (также ранее обозначавшийся как ВАЗ-2123, Chevrolet Niva и LADA Niva) — российский автомобиль повышенной проходимости ВАЗ[1]. Представляет собой второе поколение автомобилей повышенной проходимости Волжского автомобильного завода и является «преемником» модели ВАЗ-2121 «Нива». Имеет постоянный полный привод на четыре колеса, двухступенчатую раздаточную коробку и межосевой блокируемый дифференциал.

На предсерийном этапе в 1998—2002 гг. модель выпускалась на ОПП по обходным технологиям под обозначением ВАЗ-2123 «Нива».

items.name: Helga Lovekaty - SDXL
items.description:
Helga Lovekaty is a Russian fitness model, an actress, and Instagram Star. She is known for posting curvaceous pictures on her Instagram, where she has amassed more than 3.9m followers. Also, she has associated with elite Russian Modeling Agency, Mavrin Model. Besides modeling, she garnered stardom from the movie Hardcore Henry.

Notes on the file... Her mole appears correctly on simple prompts, but tends to get lost on complicated prompts (which is ok, since she covers it up in some of her modelling work). Sometimes it will make more than one mole, but that is easily fixed in inpainting as it is literally one spot.

As Miss Lovekaty is known to be curvaceous, it also defaults to cleavage. The posts here have often removed that via negative prompt, per TOS.

These pictures are base sdxl 1.0 with no refiner pass. Nor face restore or any other trick

Please let me know what you think. Any suggestions or criticism is welcome.

Part of the Women of Social Media collection

items.name: Luca Hollestelle
items.description:
Luca Hollestelle (b. 1996) is a Dutch model and actress. She has several dozen TV credits, including a long run on the Benelux show "De Ludwigs." She has utterly outstanding freckles — seriously — which Stable Diffusion doesn't pick up well in training, so if you want to be true to life, you'll want to add a freckles:1.1, 1.2, 1.3, or maybe even 1.4 to your prompt. (Though at that level and past it, you're likely to get some weird megafreckles that ruin the look.)

This embedding is based on 30 images, cooked for a total of 300 steps on base SD1.5: 16 vectors per token, a 0.004 learning rate, a batch size of 6, and 5 gradient steps.

Your ratings, especially of the five-star variety, are very much appreciated.

items.name: Melusine (Genshin Impact)
items.description:
Image posts are highly appreciated! You don't even need to leave a review. I just love to see what people are creating with my stuff.

Prompt melusine to get the character/species.

The following tags aren't necessary but shape specific species traits:

-rounded ears

-pointed ears

-thin tail

-stubby tail

-wings

-[color] skin

Melusines, the all female slug(?) species from Genshin Impact's kingdom of Fontaine. Come in a variety of colors with a few variations of body parts. Due to the lack of Melusine art, this LoRA was trained entirely on screenshots of in-game assets. This causes the default generations to be 3D looking. If you want a more 2D look you'll either need to add specific art style prompts or use a specific art style LoRA. Also due to the lack of Melusine art, this LoRA has a slight biased towards the limited number of outfits that the Melusines in-game wear by default. You'll need to put emphasis on your clothing/outfit prompts to combat this. Due to a lack of... less clothed... in-game assets, it's going to have some difficulty creating anything that requires the chest region of the body to be seen, such as a bikini. Prompting (NSFW) at high power will effectively fill in blanks for... less clothing though.

Works well with Hassaku-v1.3, AbyssOrangeMix3-A1B, Anything v4.5-pruned, and the old NAI leak.

You come across a panicking Melusine who's lost her token, so you offer to help her find it. After a combat encounter involving 3 waves of rifthounds you come across a scroll with unintelligible writings on it. When you return it to her she thanks you profusely and offers you a strange part. You ask her what the text on the scroll means and she replies, "Oh that? That's a Ko-Fi link."

items.name: Zeybek Kıyafetleri - Turkish male Aegean Clothing
items.description:
This is a model based off of re-creations of the outfit of a Zeybek, an idealized warrior from Ottoman empire that is based around the Turkish Aegean coastal area. They are more or less akin to Robin Hood and other analogous figures from different countries (i.e. help and protect the poor and vulnerable from being exploited by their higher class peers). Zeybeks are known to wear distinct outfits that set them apart from others. That distinction is shorts which is unusual for a population that is known for dressing conservatively. In addition to that, they wear a lot of weapons in their sash.

The main characteristic of the outfit is a long-sleeved jacket, shorts, a sash, and headband. If you want to use it to on a character, it's best to have knowledge about that character usual outfit or costume. For example, a character or person not known for wearing the type of clothes in this LoRa, you have to prompt it in order to be that way. Here are some examples that can be used in the prompt:

  • long-sleeved

  • shorts

  • scarf

  • headband
